                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850629-24-off112 t17850629-24-cd113"></join> last, one sack, value 4 s. and four bushels of malt, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17850629-24-victim240" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Lake
               <interp inst="t17850629-24-victim240" type="surname" value="Lake"></interp>
